Buxa,you were peace wrapped in green🌳

Just 5–6 hours from Guwahati lies Buxa Tiger Reserve, a hidden gem in North Bengal known for its dense forests, rich wildlife, and serene landscape. Start your journey by early to reach around 3 p.m, as the main gate closes at 4:30 p.m. 

For those looking to stay inside the reserve, options like <<Dooars Prakriti Homestay, Jayanti>> offer a peaceful jungle experience. Make sure to reach before gate closure if you’re staying within the forest area.

P.S. The homestay is situated deep inside the jungle, so expect occasional insects and all the tiny wild things that come with living close to nature!

#ToimoiTales #RoadTrip #WestBengal
